- backlight:
  - acpi_osi=Linux [acpi_backlight=vendor|legacy] = nv_backlight (nope)
  - acpi_osi="!Windows 2012" = nv_backlight + acpi_video0 (nope)
  - acpi_osi="!Windows 2012" acpi_backlight=vendor = nv_backlight + thinkpad_screen (nope)
  - nvidia driver = acpi_video0 (yay)

- Boot Kernel Parameters
  - thinkpad_acpi.experimental=1
  - logo.nologo
  - i915.i915_enable_rc6=3
  - i915.fastboot=1
  - loglevel=3
  - quiet nosplash
